FASTEST, MOST DIRECT AIR ROUTE
The New VIKING CLUB SHIPS
-as luxuriously comfortable and intimate as a nook of your favorite club herald a new
era in transcontinental skyway travel.
Designed and fabricated by the Lockheed Aircraft
Corporation, the VIKING CLUB SHIPS present tomorrow's speed
... tomorrow's de luxe ap-
pointments.
tomorrow's super-efficiency factors for utmost security.
This fleet of giant
speedsters streak the skylanes at 260 miles per hour top speed-cruising at 230-
-and are
universally rated the WORLD'S FASTEST TRANSPORTS.
Billowy swivel chairs are spaced
to give ample leg-room for ten 6-footer passengers and a crew of three. Hostess service,
of course! And an excellent cuisine, served in air-conditioned cabins, combine to make a
lark of the startling scenic flight over the Only Direct Route between Chicago and Seattle.
VIKING CLUB SHIPS in service, June 1937.
